name: Dcsextract
tagline: Extracts data from the DCS KA-50 and A-10c. A sample program is shown to see its operation. You can extract data for a cabin mounted. Only for 64 bit cpu
body:
### Comming soon for UH-1H

KA50: UV26, PVI, PUI, SPU9, R800, R828

A10C: CMSC, CMSP, TACAN, ILS, UHF, VHF AM, VHF FM
